room_title: Escape room "Medieval Mayhem" by Know Way Out in Petoskey
room_description: Somebody has poisoned and abducted the beloved Queen Elewys and her trusted advisor – the wizard Ortho. Time is ticking away as the poison will kill them in 60 minutes. You are Ortho’s apprentices. Quickly you must search the castle for clues to the ingredients and recipe for the antidote and save the Queen!
